                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990619-28-off159 t17990619-28-cd160"></join>, one wooden till, value 2s. 6d. and 3s. 5d. the goods, and monies numbered
            </rs>, the property of 
               <persName id="t17990619-28-victim258" type="victimName">
                  John 
                  Argent
               <interp inst="t17990619-28-victim258" type="surname" value="Argent"></interp>
